.Dd 2011-11-03  
.Dt CLUSTER-SHUTDOWN 1
.Os
.\"----------------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh NAME
.Nm cluster-shutdown
.Nd shut down the cluster in a rational order
.\"----------------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.\" Form 1
.Nm
.\"----------------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
command shuts down all compute nodes, confirms that they are down,
and then optionally shuts down the head node.
.Pp
The user is prompted for the grace period and other options.
.\"----------------------------------------------------------------------
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.\"----------------------------------------------------------------------
